<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<style>
.logopic {
  height: 40px;
  width: 55px;
}
.moreinfo {
  color: #d4d4d4;
  font-size: 13px;
}
.moreinfo a{
  color: #d4d4d4;
}
.divide {
  width: 250px;
}
body {
  background-color: #dbdbdb;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<center><img src="https://www.blurrmc.com/images/Blurr_Logo.png" alt="Blurr Logo" class="logopic">
<h3>Hello<%= @email %></h3>
<div>
  <% if @resource.try(:unconfirmed_email?) %>
    <h4>We're here to notify you that your email is being changed to <%= @resource.unconfirmed_email %>.</h4>
  <% else %>
    <h4>We're here to notify you that your email has been changed to <%= @resource.email %>.</h4>
  <% end %>
</div>
<hr class="divide">
<p class="moreinfo">You are receiving this email because you signed up with <a href="https://www.blurrmc.com">BlurrMC</a></p>
<p class="moreinfo">This email was sent to <%= @email %></p>
<p class="moreinfo">Didn't change your email? Contact us at <a href="contact@blurrmc.com">contact@blurrmc.com</a></p>
<p class="moreinfo">Â© <%= Date.today.year %> <strong>Martin Velev</strong></p>/center>
</body>
</html>
